{"tid":1506772,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[濕L晒，你要驚]防毒濾棉濕哂水會打柴，請立即更換","createTime":"2019-08-26T02:06:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T13:32:09.000Z","uid":50904,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"2f64a8acd12ebcd6f1460ad49ce590c796a1172c","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:06:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">利申:唔係呢方面專家，只係問人+整合資料，需要人實測</span><br />\n<br />\n琴日落左成日大雨，好多裝修師傅都被迫做左海底奇兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然濾棉有一定「抗水」能力去過濾有毒蒸汽，但係「唉屌濕撚晒」之下都會打柴<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為防TL;DR 先寫結論:</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 外露濾棉如 2297/2097 + 單罐豬嘴3311K 等，如濕哂請即更換<br />\n2. 如501蓋 + 5N11 有外殼包下嘅，請打開檢查有無全濕<br />\n3. 內置濾棉嘅綜合濾罐 如60926/3系列，正路入水位唔多，但好睇實際有幾濕<br />\n4. 單純濾罐部份 如6006/3 系列，活性碳唔吸水，乾返應該唔大影響，有待實測<br />\n5. 雨天環境，重課可考慮502蓋 + 3M 7093 有殼防水式P100濾棉"},{"pid":"babf1ed6b1174b2db6f517d464e552dc6f9436ed","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:07:13.000Z","msg":"正文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2297 / 2097 / 5N11 / 3311K 等嘅濾棉入邊其實用人做纖維(即係膠，類似環保袋嘅不織布)黎過濾有毒微粒，所以應付濕氣理論上係無問題<br />\n<br />\n之但係琴日咁全濕之下，可能會令啲濾棉痴埋一舊，一黎過令濾效能減低，二黎有機會減低透氣度，所以就算乾返都未必有用<br />\n<br />\n至於濾罐入邊主要成份係活性碳，佢係一啲好多孔嘅結構，佢係靠「吸附」即係痴住啲有機毒氣粒子去物運作，而唔係好似海綿吸水式咁「吸收」，所以理論上濕過水整返乾唔影響佢效能<br />\n<br />\n你可能會問，但琴日我濕L晒咁用落都無問題wo? 原因好可能由於:<br />\n1.「催淚彈」隻化合物本身唔溶係水嘅，濕水返而令你有啲保護<br />\n2. 大雨阻止左啲有毒微粒散佈，好似地盤灑水防塵咁<br />\n3. 雨水令催淚彈溫度下降，減少低毒氣同微粒擴散<br />\n所以唔好咁老定住，下次好天你重用可能就會出事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3M有出一隻有外殼嘅防水式P100濾棉，7093，但一黎貴、二黎係咪真係咁多雨天裝修機會無人知，有能力嘅可以考慮入手，但留意需要502蓋接駁(據講曾經一度無貨/話會停產)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0TsM92p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0TsM92p.jpg&h=41227a51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDigikey賣緊$45一邊，見其他炒價去到$150一對都有，自已衡量下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.digikey.hk/product-detail/zh/3m/7093/3M160510-ND/6827875\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.digikey.hk%2Fproduct-detail%2Fzh%2F3m%2F7093%2F3M160510-ND%2F6827875&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxiHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=ab1f4b11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.digikey.hk/product-detail/zh/3m/7093/3M160510-ND/6827875</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總合我個人9估雨天裝修防水組合排名<br />\n1: 6006/3濾罐 + 502蓋 + 7093防水有殼濾綿<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0TsM92p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0TsM92p.jpg&h=41227a51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 60926/3系列、內置P100綿綜合濾罐<br />\n有外殼+入水位相對較小，但如全濕只能成個換<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cCTc5Bi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcCTc5Bi.jpg&h=e214ab68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 6006/3濾罐  + 501蓋 + 5N11濾綿 <br />\n501蓋係有包住下，但個洞都幾大，加上5N11只係P95 級，但勝在可留濾罐乾左重用(待實測)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pmj0u2r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPmj0u2r.jpg&h=2fb73a75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 6006/3濾罐  + 502蓋 + 2297/2097濾綿<br />\n濾綿完全野外露出，大雨就GG，可留濾罐乾左重用(待實測)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yuOXxgS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyuOXxgS.jpg&h=30e3fe8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTzzzvd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTzzzvd.jpg&h=88b22160&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5. 3200單罐豬嘴用3311K，大面積吸水加不可拆，應該全面GG<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rFZDgJC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrFZDgJC.jpg&h=2c9f06d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efd74f08c4e975e75d6aad88cf7c29fff20b2122","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:07:46.000Z","msg":"自推10連比更多人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42e874770a9135f67a25937173fa32553c2e2f2","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:07:56.000Z","msg":"9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68c9c1bb4a289dfd76622c4d37fb73b26445eff","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:08:08.000Z","msg":"8<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"908229bb1120b8c2d42462e525d1bb8877184c57","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:14:34.000Z","msg":"爭啲唔記得想講<br />\n縱然傍陀大雨，都無法熄滅香港人爭取自由民主嘅熱血<br />\n無和理勇武之分，只有企前企後之別<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />地方的義士們需要更多鼓勵同歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=77xWR0agV2I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D77xWR0agV2I&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxiHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=1333fbe8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=77xWR0agV2I</a>"},{"pid":"67adba797e00ecfd29f312c861a1f5d4a5e6e9e5","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:14:48.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"5b88bcc3eaf331eec491777626c717511a288ddd","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:14:58.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"f4196261c717f87446fd75f1d2533191d562b09c","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:15:08.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"2f0ad41b08491b25528926b63d9dd8522709be4d","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:15:18.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"30d2d1807fb96390dcdd9cc2384924c031befdcb","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:15:28.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"f580aef2da5537cd72f8ae1cdc5e53f04f695ae4","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:15:38.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"89fd1e1b551249861432b473684bb4173220d30b","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:31:17.000Z","msg":"完全無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再自推幾野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f297fdd5d51aad4d8f078069efc433fb0123b84","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:31:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90fa4c5a8c3f46cf04748ace7871db23c59fda7c","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:31:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72470bc02f529025771519cbe294990c7e16c145","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:31:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e296afb8ae2100a26bf0e534c4c449b9196c8188","tid":1506772,"uid":67392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:40:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"624f7c65a9de8c3fe47aded23457da93c1cdbdb1","tid":1506772,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:46:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"379548fbef0899d45f7266d993ed6dba6d64ba60","tid":1506772,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:57:18.000Z","msg":"用保鮮紙包住淚罐, 保鮮紙開返少少透氣位得唔得"},{"pid":"2690faf12566cf6fb03c2216ebcd50a13ba06851","tid":1506772,"uid":118228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:58:28.000Z","msg":"60926唔係防水架咩?"},{"pid":"e84b518356cb44577668a3b596846719deb5b5e1","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:03:15.000Z","msg":"另外再次提醒<br />\nTear Gas係極微細有毒粉末 + 毒煙，就算煙啲粉末都係會痴住，所以大家一定要著長衫長褲<br />\n<br />\n同埋要分開清洗受污染嘅衣物同防護裝備，記得帶返醫用/膠手套去處理，可以先過轉清水/浸一浸先用洗衣機洗<br />\n<br />\n豬嘴用後都需要清潔一下，拆走濾罐之後用水刷下，唔好用酒精濕紙巾抹，會減少個豬嘴啲膠嘅壽命<br />\n<br />\n可參考3M官方豬嘴清潔教學，<br />\nStep 2 消毒我諗非必要，但入邊成日焗汗可能都會有細菌，<br />\n佢係用大約1:99稀釋漂白水洗去消毒，即1ml 漂白水 就加 99ml清水，大約咁上下啦，總之唔好太重手搞到好大味<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mlWyMPFwEI8&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmlWyMPFwEI8%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26t%3D731&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxiHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=d102c95c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mlWyMPFwEI8&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=731</a>"},{"pid":"c47e1b3476a560d41a1107a372259ccc3c890310","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2690faf12566cf6fb03c2216ebcd50a13ba06851","tid":1506772,"uid":118228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:58:28.000Z","msg":"60926唔係防水架咩?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:08:30.000Z","msg":"所有濾棉都抗水&quot;water resistant&quot; ，可防濕氣，但唔係預你浸濕哂果種防水&quot;water proof&quot;<br />\n<br />\n60926係將塊濾棉放埋入盒，但你都見始終有啲la去氣<br />\n琴日咁大雨，好睇實際上有幾濕"},{"pid":"633d0b7170d282dac0a47833fcc86025627ff371","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"379548fbef0899d45f7266d993ed6dba6d64ba60","tid":1506772,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:57:18.000Z","msg":"用保鮮紙包住淚罐, 保鮮紙開返少少透氣位得唔得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:11:20.000Z","msg":"無研究過，要靠大家實測下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗主係考慮會唔會搞到唔通氣，呼吸無咁順<br />\n總之如果你開始由無味變到有味，或者呼叫唔順就要換"},{"pid":"26007863c1fe5d2c08ea6e80537ea80a5177963b","tid":1506772,"uid":80904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc49d4a00c1a4adca8e1aca4e82018441d0cc63","tid":1506772,"uid":226103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:16:41.000Z","msg":"推有用文"},{"pid":"3289b98ecf51696cc21be06cf70995d7b51a735d","tid":1506772,"uid":144787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:18:52.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"e3a56be096e470b83f6b195d46e1f1cef2e5d1c7","tid":1506772,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:24:08.000Z","msg":"必須將新疆燈柱未成形前，連根拔起。行動方案討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506499</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b9d9123280f8c199f2fd28068ec914194adcbc94","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26007863c1fe5d2c08ea6e80537ea80a5177963b","tid":1506772,"uid":80904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41687b89084f1e1ae25904244ee0bf6ffad673f8","tid":1506772,"uid":209888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:27:05.000Z","msg":"裝修佬請睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7559df12930d575d098cdf8312d5bcf47562b6","tid":1506772,"uid":80904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9d9123280f8c199f2fd28068ec914194adcbc94","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26007863c1fe5d2c08ea6e80537ea80a5177963b","tid":1506772,"uid":80904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma