T04:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38279d491b97391d1fd7504d70e6e55f65b8727","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:36:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da9126a5a07e305ffe5a915e1ca3e20fd55353eb","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91701ec8a772c871267048387d005f55443f2a8c","tid":1506772,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:36:23.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogleDrive: 91機場文宣資源 (手足有新貨話我知，會Upload上去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxiHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=fc141684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n----------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>英文文宣建議：</strong></span><br />\n內容:<br />\n91 Hong Kong International Airport<br />\nSOS: Humanitarian Crisis Alert<br />\nGovernment has failed us. Police shot us.<br />\nIt&rsquo;s now or never, please stand with HK.<br />\nThanks in advance for your support and understanding.<br />\n<br />\n方向/ 建議：<br />\n-強調事態之緊急及嚴重<br />\n-形式係事先通知，而非道歉，機場示威是出師有名同埋其中既正當性<br />\n-例如可用&rdquo;SOS&rdquo;之字眼<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kZESP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3kZESP.jpg&h=ba0a90fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLLrqSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLLrqSL.jpg&h=724c5863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cf0e3065c35586a3aa97b1f7d7e3887721b0b14","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:36:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c6eea127c88b4bf6f894f25aa6f436bcb4cd53","tid":1506772,"uid":310966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:37:24.000Z","msg":"推阿 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b00acadde6b52275a4248f6587bc75bd0e78541","tid":1506772,"uid":234597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:37:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3e1fb7bf15f157d57f0cde8db3eef1714a3d9c2","tid":1506772,"uid":131767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:59:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e643bd684b96a54188052d4d3d6c47be215737","tid":1506772,"uid":100363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:05:07.000Z","msg":"推 五大訴求 缺一不可 打狗救人 825荃葵青遊行 831劍指中聯辦 9月1參觀機場 9月2罷課 721 85 811警黑勾結無法無天"},{"pid":"92f0a54c6f812ad94398892489f9bab9c58b758b","tid":1506772,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:10:08.000Z","msg":"人手頂置<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b75b998c26b3023d94b10bd4d0805390054bfb","tid":1506772,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:34:21.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}